comments.message:
if I remember right, dbusConnection is a shared_ptr, because it needs to be shared among all the various sensors in this daemon.  In theory, it's really a singleton, and we could probably move to a pattern like

static DbusConnection& getDbus(){
    static DbusConnection;
    return DbusConnection;
} 

So we can avoid passing the connection around everywhere, but that would be for a future refactoring.
